dc_description_s: This data layer represents parcels for Jackson County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Jackson_Parcels_2015.gdb. [Parcels of Jackson County, WI. The parcel layer was originally created in shapefile format by ProWest. They were imported to a feature class in Aug 2007. Features are based on deeds, surveys, and other legal documents. This dataset is updated continually as ownership and boundary lines change.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
